<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Why Start a Chapter</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">Make a difference in your community. Build leadership skills. Help close the digital divide.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Empower Your Community</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Lead free tech education programs that help seniors and underserved groups learn how to use devices, browse the internet safely, and stay connected with family.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Gain Real-World Experience</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Running a chapter means organizing events, leading sessions, and working with real people — experience that matters on college applications, resumes, and in life.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">We'll Support You Every Step</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You're not doing this alone. We provide branding, lesson plans, outreach templates, and guidance to help you launch and grow your chapter successfully.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">What Our Community Says</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8" x-data="{ activeSlide: 0 }">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8" x-show="activeSlide === 0">
          <blockquote class="text-gray-600 italic">
            "I never thought I'd learn to use my phone. Now I video call my daughter every weekend."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-medium">— Resident, Arbor Terrace Senior Living</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8" x-show="activeSlide === 1">
          <blockquote class="text-gray-600 italic">
            "These classes helped me feel more independent. I finally understand how to shop online and avoid scams."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-900 font-medium">— Program Attendee</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-span-2 flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-8">
          <button 
            class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" 
            :class="{ 'bg-blue-500': activeSlide === 0 }"
            @click="activeSlide = 0"
          ></button>
          <button 
            class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" 
            :class="{ 'bg-blue-500': activeSlide === 1 }"
            @click="activeSlide = 1"
          ></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Initialize Alpine.js
  import Alpine from 'alpinejs';
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const alpine = Alpine;
    alpine.start();
  });
</script> 